brary of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.141635, "shard": "05", "shelf_id": "2010270509, 1930-12-11, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/nbu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["nebraska", "holt county (neb.)", "holt county", "o'neill (neb.)", "holt", "newspapers", "o'neill city", "o'neill", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["O'Neill (Neb.)--Newspapers", "Holt County (Neb.)--Newspapers", "Nebraska--Holt County", "Nebraska--O'Neill", "United States--Nebraska--Holt--O'Neill", "United States--Nebraska--Holt--O'Neill City"], "subjects": [{"holt": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:holt&fo=json"}, {"holt county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:holt+county&fo=json"}, {"holt county (neb.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:holt+county+%28neb.%29&fo=json"}, {"nebraska": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:nebraska&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"o'neill": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:o%27neill&fo=json"}, {"o'neill (neb.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:o%27neill+%28neb.%29&fo=json"}, {"o'neill city": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:o%27neill+city&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2025-12-14T17:22:02.922Z", "title": "The frontier (O'Neill City, Holt County, Neb.), December 11, 1930", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2010270509/1930-12-11/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2010270509/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/2010270509", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/33e9ff77-2c63-5ec5-a74e-d387b2ba2ae5"], "batch": ["nbu_americanrobin_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1880", "description": ["Weekly Began in 1880; ceased with v. 85, no. 6 (May 27, 1965). Some sections titled: Frontier and Verdigre eagle, May 14-Nov. 26, 1964. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Absorbed: Item (O'Neill, Neb.), 1892; Verdigre eagle (Verdigre, Neb. : 1931), 1964; Stuart advocate, 1965. Merged with: Holt County independent (O'Neill, Neb. : 1897), to form: Frontier and Holt County independent. Description based on: [Vol. 1], no. 10 (Sept. 30, 1880); title from masthead. Latest issue consulted: Vol. 85, no. 6 (May 27, 1965). Holt County independent (O'Neill, Neb. : 1897) Frontier and Holt County independent"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:16.670Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-10", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-10"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2010270509/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [42.457652, -98.647789], "location": ["nebraska", "holt county", "holt", "o'neill city", "o'neill", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-98.647789, 42.457652], "number": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2010270509/1963-06-20/ed-1/", "660034186", "online resource", "http://www.loc.gov/item/2010270509/1880-09-30/ed-1/", "2026-05-01t10:47:40.600000", "2010270509", "4082", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2025-05-23t21:30:26", "1", "2768-5799"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Publisher's box title: O'Neill frontier"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division", "the frontier (o'neill city, holt county, neb.) 1880-1965", "catalog", "chronicling america"]