utor": ["university of nebraska-lincoln libraries, lincoln, ne"], "date": "1930-12-11", "dates": ["1930-12-11"], "description": ["Dont u to m simp BOT if you must convince your self try some ordinary tobacco in an old pipe Note result in chalk on the bottom of your left shoe Then try some ordinary tobacco in your favorite pipe Note on other boe Finally try some Sir Walter Raleigh smoking tobacco in any good pipe You wont have to note it any where for youll notice with the very jfirst puff how much cooler and milder lit it It stays so right down to the last puff in the bowlrich mellow and fragrant Your regular tobacco nist has Sir Walter of course Try a tin today ITS 15and milder Hard to Figure Reason for His Staying Away Women get away with murder remarked Jack Doyle fight promoter because it is generally understood tiiut they dont mean what they say This always gives them a loophole when things go wrong Fuany part of it is that the wom en themselves do not seem to think their remarks should be taken literal ly Like Gwenny Whats the trouble between you and Freddie a friend asked her Im sure I dont know said Gwenny He hasnt been to see me for a"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-12-01T12:38:40.636Z", "group": ["ndnp/nbu", "university-of-nebraska-of-nebraska-lincoln-libraries-lincoln-ne-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/2010270509/1930-12-11/ed-1/?sp=7", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:nbu:batch_nbu_devilscorkscrew_ver04:data:2010270509:00279527677:1930121101:1042/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=483&w=335", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:nbu:batch_nbu_devilscorkscrew_ver04:data:2010270509:00279527677:1930121101:1042/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=966&w=671", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/nbu/batch_nbu_devilscorkscrew_ver04/data/2010270509/00279527677/1930121101/1042.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 7, "language":